metadata.name: Fear of the unknown
metadata.description: The goddess has passed into another world, into another dimension or space. She recognized this world and went to explore other worlds. The little deer is her carefree companion, he was left alone, he is scared, he is frightened by the unknown, he could not cover with his mind the finiteness of the existing world, accept the transition and go further with the Goddess. He is confused, he is lonely, he is afraid of the unknown, he is scared.
